sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer App
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant B as Booking Service
    participant R as Ride Service
    participant D as Driver Service
    participant P as Pricing Service
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant N as Notification Service

    C->>G: Tao booking
    G->>P: Uoc tinh gia
    P-->>G: Fare estimate
    G->>B: Luu booking
    B-->>G: Booking confirmed
    G-->>C: Tra booking result

    B->>MQ: booking confirmed event
    MQ->>R: Kich hoat tao ride
    R->>MQ: ride.finding_driver_requested
    MQ->>G: Realtime matching event
    G->>D: Tim driver online gan nhat
    G-->>D: NEW_RIDE_AVAILABLE qua socket

    D->>G: Driver accept
    G->>R: driverAcceptOfferedRide
    R->>MQ: ride.assigned / ride.accepted
    MQ->>G: Fan-out status update
    G-->>C: RIDE_STATUS_UPDATE

    R->>MQ: ride.completed
    MQ->>N: Tao notification
